SUMMARY:WordPress Hangout & Networking
DESCRIPTION:WordPress Montclair Meetup\nCome to network\, chat\, talk shop
 \, or just hang out with like-minded WordPress folks. Alcoholic\\* and non
 -alcoholic beverages\, along with a variety of food options will be availa
 ble to purchase. Hope to see you there!\n\nWe will be meeting at Just Jake
 's in the backroom area.\n\n\\*Please be safe and no drinking to excess.\n
 \n\\-\\-\\-\nJoin the **JerseyPress Slack** group to chat with others in o
 ur community and get help: [https://jerseypress.org/slack/](https://jersey
 press.org/slack/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/events/311
 737792/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251027T205409Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251027T205409Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_311737673@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260316T013537Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260402T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260402T200000
SUMMARY:Help Desk - Bring Your Laptop\, Yourself\, and Your WordPress Prob
 lems
DESCRIPTION:WordPress Montclair Meetup\nIf you are running a WordPress sit
 e and are having issues and would like some help\, then this Meetup is for
  you!\n\nIf you know some things\, expert or not\, and want to give back t
 o the WordPress community\, then this Meetup is for you too!\n\nWe will do
  our best to match a problem with a problem-solver. On-site and in real-ti
 me. Just bring yourself\, your laptop\, and your WordPress problems.\n\nIt
 's OK if you attend and only want to observe. We recognize this is how peo
 ple learn. Given our time limit of two hours\, we may not be able to solve
  everyone's issues\, but we will try! If you are seeking help\, please com
 e prepared. Have your web site loaded in a browser\, have your WordPress a
 dmin ready\, along with a short list of issues you are trying to solve.\n\
 nPeople helping are volunteers and may not be experts. There is risk to br
 eaking your site! Please do not bring client or business sites that can im
 pact reputations or revenue. If you have a staging site we can test things
  with\, that is always preferred. If it is a production site\, please crea
 te a site backup before having someone do any work on your site.\n\n**New 
 Venue**:\nRecRoom is a welcoming coworking + community space inside the ne
 wly re-opened Lackawanna Station in Montclair\, NJ.\n\nMore information ab
 out the venue can be found here: [https://recroomnj.com/faqs](https://recr
 oomnj.com/faqs)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\nJoin the **JerseyPress Slack** group to chat
  with others in our community and get help: [https://jerseypress.org/slack
 /](https://jerseypress.org/slack/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/events/311
 737673/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251027T204341Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251027T204341Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
